skdetail:
Rated: Guidance Suggested. This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: history quiz
des:
Hey there, are you looking for a game which is fun to play and also educates you in learning new things in the process. Well, you have come to the right place. Our skill aims to help people learn more about the world history using a fun quiz. 

How to play:
1. You will be asked a question . Each question will have multiple choice answers.
 2.To give your answer, repeat the number of the option(one, two, three etc.) .
3. After each set of questions, you will be given a score and the game will end.
4. You can play again, to get a new set of questions.
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
